{"tid":2492603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冰島宣佈制裁中國","createTime":"2021-04-17T08:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T08:48:04.000Z","uid":125168,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"54392393216af49c35dc243193ca7736fd8dfdbc","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:42:54.000Z","msg":"冰島跟隨歐盟就新疆問題制裁中方 北京制裁冰島律師反制<br />\n<br />\n冰島跟隨歐盟，就新疆人權問題制裁中國個人和實體，引起中方不滿，召見冰島駐華大使抗議。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐冰島大使館發聲明，批評冰島的做法違反國際法，嚴重損害雙邊關係，決定對冰島相關人員實施同等制裁。冰島傳媒報道，被制裁的是當地一名律師，曾經在報章撰文批評中國，已經被中國列入黑名單，是冰島目前唯一被中國制裁的人。冰島外交部長對有公民被制裁感到驚訝，認為他只是行使憲法賦予的言論自由，對中方制裁表示抗議。 <br />\n<br />\n外電報道，這名律師所寫的文章，去年10月已刊登，主要批評中國使館擁有的房地產問題、中國在全球疫情大流行的角色、以及中國遊客的問題等。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/china/2387649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2387649&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=e24d843b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/china/2387649</a>"},{"pid":"e10a7ed39952bf195e8a716b09e6999beb8eb1d8","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:43:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C4pHKSX6wRA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC4pHKSX6wRA&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=3e83ae6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C4pHKSX6wRA</a>"},{"pid":"577439a43035f829fb6f221a5af5f65b4e3ee9dd","tid":2492603,"uid":308440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"又加速"},{"pid":"7f24395ec5d780817776186e77d398ae93f8f04d","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"577439a43035f829fb6f221a5af5f65b4e3ee9dd","tid":2492603,"uid":308440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"又加速"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4587958d03bb18fa69ba9065d2985442732c2dc2","tid":2492603,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:44:36.000Z","msg":"仲有邊個未<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd1faa9b66739f749a991498801d47e5cd5d1dd","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96abc173809c985ef4182a09f3180dd145588d03","tid":2492603,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地制裁你<br />\n<br />\n你就搵個律師制裁"},{"pid":"7aa99722d15922c774b884c53a538a57be3775c4","tid":2492603,"uid":201398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"msi lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57ea83d6f013198614c93028d52bf994e340d40","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b534403dc07e64427fb329911baf7e9dfb63e95","tid":2492603,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:47:29.000Z","msg":"錯不在大使館、国家及人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e628bce196e2d70c09fae6970a7fa63516efad","tid":2492603,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}